\c 9
\s Kusatenda kwavaJudha nokurashwa kwavo
\p
\v 1 Ndinotaura zvirokwazvo munaKristu, handirevi nhema, hana yangu ichindipupurira muMweya Mutsvene,
\v 2 kuti ndinoshushikana kwazvo nokushungurudzika kusingaperi mumoyo mangu.
\v 3 Nokuti ndaida kuti ini ndimene ndive munhu wakatukwa kunaKristu Jesu wakaparadzaniswa nokuda kwehama dzangu, ivo vorudzi rwangu panyama;
\v 4 ndivo vaIsraeri vane kuitwa vana nokubwinya nesungano nokupiwa murairo, nokushumira, nezvipikirwa;
\v 5 madzibaba ndaavo, naKristu wakabva kwavari panyama, uye uri pamusoro pavose, Mwari unokudzwa nokusingaperi. Ameni.
\v 6 Kwete shoko raMwari serakashaya basa. Nokuti vakabva kuvaIsraeri havazi vaIsraeri vose;
\v 7 Kananokuti vose vanozvarwa naAbhurahamu havazi vana, asi \add zvinonzi\add*: KunaIsaka ndiko kuchatumidzwa rudzi rwako.
\v 8 Ndokuti: Avo vari vana venyama havazi vana vaMwari; asi vana vechipikirwa, ndivo vanonzi zvizvarwa.
\v 9 Nokuti iri shoko rechipikirwa \add rinoti\add*: Nenguva ino ndichavuya, uye Sara uchava nomwanakomana.
\v 10 Hazvizi izvozvo chete; asi Rebekavo, wakati ava nemimba kunomumwe, iye Isaka, baba vedu;
\v 11 nokuti vasati vaberekwa, vasati vaita zvakanaka kana zvakaipa, kuti kufunga kwaMwari maererano nesananguro vasimbiswe, kwete namabasa, asi naiye unodana,
\v 12 zvakanzi kwaari: Mukuru uchashumira mudoko.
\v 13 Sezvazvakanyorwa, zvichinzi: Jakobho ndakamuda, asi Esau ndakamuvenga.
\v 14 Zvino tichatiyiko? Kusarurama kuripo kunaMwari here? NgazvisadaroHaiswa!
\v 15 Nokuti unoti kunaMozisi: Ndichanzwira ngoni wandinonzwira ngoni, ndichanzwira tsitsi wandinonzwira tsitsi.
\v 16 Naizvozvo hazvibvi kunounoda, kana kunounomhanya, asi kunaMwari, munzwiri wengoni.
\v 17 Nokuti Rugwaro runoti kunaFarao: Ndizvo zvandakakumutsira, kuti zita rangu riparidzwe panyika yose.
\v 18 Naizvozvo unonzwira ngoni waanoda; uye unowomesera moyo waanoda.
\v 19 Zvino iwe ungati kwandiri: Iye uchapireiko mhosva? Nokuti ndianiko unoramba kuda kwake?
\v 20 Ko zvino iwe munhu, ndiwe aniko, unopindura Mwari? Ko chakavumbwa chingati kunowakachivumba: Wandiitireiko kudai?
\v 21 Ko muvumbi wehari haanesimba pamusoro pevhu here, kuti nebundu rimwe aite mudziyo mumwe wakakudzwa, nomumwe usina kukudzwa?
\v 22 Zvino tichatiyiko kana Mwari, kana akanga achida kuratidza kutsamwa kwake, nokuzivisa simba rake, akaita nomoyo murefu zvikuru pamusoro pemidziyo yokutsamwirwa, yakagadzirirwa kuparadzwa,
\v 23 kuti azivise kufuma kokubwinya kwake pamusoro pemidziyo yengoni, yaakanga agadzirira kubwinya,
\v 24 iyesu vakadamwavo naye, tisingabvi kuvaJudha bedzi, asi kuvahedhenivo?
\v 25 Sezvaanorevavo pabhuku yaHosiya, achiti: Avo vakanga vasi vanhu vangu; Ndichavaidza vanhu vangu; Naiye wakanga asi mudikamwa, ndichamuidza mudikamwa.
\v 26 Zvichaitika kuti paya pakanga parebwa kwavari: Hamuzi vanhu vangu, Ipapo vachaidzwa vanakomana vaMwari mupenyu.
\v 27 NaIsaya unodana pamusoro pavaIsraeri achiti kunyange kuwanda kwavana vaIsraeri kwakaita sejecha regungwa, vakasara vachaponeswa;
\v 28 nokuti Ishe uchaita panyika shoko rake, nokuripedzisa, nokukurumidza nokururama.
\v 29 Sezvaakamboreva Isayavo, achiti: Dai Ishe wehondo asina kutisiyira rudzi, Tingadai takava seSodhoma, takaitwa seGomora.
\v 30 Zvino tichatiyiko? Tichati, vahedheni vasina kutsvaka kururama, ndivo vakawana kururama, iko kururama kokutenda;
\v 31 asi vaIsraeri vakati vachitsvaka murairo wokururama havana kusvika pamurairo wokururama.
\v 32 Neiko? Nokuti havana kutsvaka nokutenda, asi zvinenge namabasa omurairo. Vakagumburwa nebwe rinogumbusa.
\v 33 Sezvazvakanyorwa, zvichinzi: Tarira, ndinoisa paZiyoni ibwe rokugumbusa, nedombo rokupinganidza; Unotenda kwaari, haanganyadziswi.
